thread.title: JOHNATHON DUNCAN
thread.title_full: Oak Motors reviewed by JOHNATHON DUNCAN

author: JOHNATHON DUNCAN
title: JOHNATHON DUNCAN
text: I went in saturday morning to see about trading in my old car. Left there a very happy customer. Left the lot with a nice 2006 pontiac grand prix and brought my 99 grand prix home as well for only 200 down. For anyone who goes to oak motors on 38th i highly recommend you see Ryan. If i couod give more than 5 stars i would.
